{"tid":351574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被兼職去支那傳單、病假罰$300","createTime":"2017-08-08T07:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T07:50:22.000Z","uid":36502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92367efd6a94dd81254af2225292ab32e6d034f1","tid":351574,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"屯門的興德學校，多次因為校長陳章萍的管理手法而見報，包括要求教師調堂，再前往深圳派傳單，又在教員室及茶水間安裝閉路電視，而片段會連接到陳校長的手機，引起教職員不滿。陳校長又要求每位教師每請一日病假，需要交出6張餅卡或300元，以「慶祝自己病癒」。學校管理問題多多，教育局近月終於正式介入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/110394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F110394&d=gdiYxCtBTdaFGM%2Brub%2BvXAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7e1e96b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/110394</a>"},{"pid":"f135a75eadbe2b23b8678edcf3c81388a9945a1e","tid":351574,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:25:46.000Z","msg":"所以話學校校長根本係土皇帝"},{"pid":"f4a5730a6f87bc87f7f4ab5e6b00f82c8e1c3c9d","tid":351574,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"都痂撚線，假設個老師真係病，睇完一日醫生俾咗兩百仲要俾三百佢，病一日支出大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}